<lb n="3" break="no"/>kkoṟṟappāṭi <unclear>na</unclear>ṉ<supplied reason="omitted">c</supplied><hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> viḷainilattu viṭṭa nilam Aiñcu v<unclear>e</unclear>liyu<supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied> Iṉnilattukku viṭṭa kuṭi Aiñcāl vanta puṉcey nilamum Ikkuṭi Aiñcāl vanta Iṟai
